            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>花旗集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:C:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/C\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">C-US</a>)截至台北時間09日02:47股價上漲5.95美元，報123.08美元，漲幅5.08%，成交量10,391,625（股），盤中最高價124.49美元、最低價121.73美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+2.42%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+2.13%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+2.42%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+5.57%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>花旗集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:C:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/C\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">C-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+3.28%</li> <li>近 1 月：+9.95%</li> <li>近 3 月：-3.49%</li> <li>近 6 月：+19.76%</li> <li>今年以來：+0.38%</li></ul></section></main>",
